<i>in a calm and orderly fashion.</i>

1069
01:31:00,200 --> 01:31:03,568
<i>Additional food,
medicine and clothing</i>

1070
01:31:03,640 --> 01:31:05,961
<i>will be provided upon arrival.</i>

1071
